name: JUNGLE SAFARI
description: Embark on an immersive adventure with your chosen group, whether it’s a small gathering, or a larger team. Our escape rooms are family-friendly and fun for everyone. Are you ready for an adventure? All rooms have color based puzzles.

name: Jungle Safari
description: Discover diverse adventures in our escape rooms. With multiple themed spaces and exciting puzzles, it’s perfect for group fun, team building and birthday parties!
location: 130 Dundas Street West, 3rd Floor Toronto, Ontario, M5G 1C3

name: Jungle
description: A non-scary escape room set in a jungle theme.

name: The Lost Treasure
description: Find clues and solve puzzles to uncover hidden treasures in this adventure-filled escape room.

name: The Exorcist
description: News has spread of a small child trapped in an old, mysterious house. Evil is lurking in every corner. You hear a cry for help, so you and your friends run in to save the child, but you notice something is not right with this house. You hear strange noises. You are not alone. Something dark is lurking in the shadows. Will you save the child in time? This room has puzzles feature color elements, is a dark room.

name: The Godfather
description: You are a member of the Corleone mafia family – one of the most powerful families in the Big Apple until now. Dark times have come to the Corleone family, and you need a way out before they take you out with the trash. You and your mafia members need a backup plan so you decide to work for the new and prosperous Tattaglia mafia family. To deserve their trust, you must complete a dangerous task – steal the Corleone’s diary. You have 60 minutes before anyone finds out. Will you make it out alive? Or will you be sleeping with the fishes?

name: The Red Admiral
description: The cold war has yet to end, as the battle for political and military power heightened tensions between the East and the West. Information is the key to prevailing in the ongoing struggles. You are tasked with collecting data along with your team of top secret spies. Today, you are given an opportunity to end the war. Your cover has allowed you to slip past security; now, the Enemy’s Admiral wishes to meet face to face with your team.

name: The Penitentiary
description: You suddenly wake up to find yourself locked in a cramped prison cell, cold, scared, the air-filled with silence. You soon realize that you are in the St. Temple Prison. This abandoned prison has a history of mysteriously taking the lives of its prisoners. If you don’t want to be next, you have to escape...

name: The Kingdom of Cats
description: The Cat King has been Catnapped! He vanished from his room one day and has been missing ever since! The whole royal family is scratching their ears as they search for their beloved King to no avail. You have been invited to a tea party by the Queen, as you are the greatest detectives in the human world. Will you be able to find the King and save the Cat Kingdom from falling into chaos?

name: The Ninja
description: This room requires you to remove your shoes before entering the dojo. After years of training under Master Fuma Kotaro, your final test is here. To prove your skills, work together to solve Master Kotaro’s puzzles hidden in the Dojo. Your mission: find the ninja headbands within 60 minutes to become full-fledged Shinobis. Join the adventure and immerse yourself in the challenge where teamwork and cunning are your keys to success.

name: The Prisoner
description: You and your friends have been wrongly accused of murder, facing an impending death sentence. Dive into a thrilling escape quest, delving into the prison’s history of successful breakouts. Collaborate with your team, leveraging the clues left behind, to mastermind a daring breakout for all inmates. With just 60 minutes before the guards escort you to execution, this immersive experience challenges your group’s teamwork and quick thinking.

name: The Champion of Dragons
description: Had so much fun here! Did the butcher room with myself and one other friend and managed to escape... Great way to spend an afternoon.

name: The Butcher’s Room
description: Did the butcher’s room, the set design was superb! I’ve done a couple escape rooms in different cities and I’m always disoriented on what I can and cannot do and sometimes the exercises can be so convoluted. This one was my favourite by far as it’s straightforward. We almost made it within the hour but this room was more like a 3/5 difficulty if you keep a clear mind despite all the horror.

name: The Butcher's Basement
description: Did the butcher’s room, the set design was superb! I’ve done a couple escape rooms in different cities and I’m always disoriented on what I can and cannot do and sometimes the exercises can be so convoluted. This one was my favourite by far as it’s straightforward... The puzzles were fun/interesting to solve — always looking for codes/number patterns so we could unlock the next room and progress. The creepy props all around always kept me wondering, 'what's a clue, what isn't?' adding to the fun, suspense, and mystery of it all.

name: The Prisoner Max 9 Players 60 Min Family Friendly
The Mystery of the Lost Ship
description: You find yourselves in a mysterious room filled with ancient artifacts. Your mission: solve the puzzles and find the key to escape before time runs out.

name: The 13th Exit
description: It’s below In a long-forgotten mansion hidden by time, a group stumbles upon an adventure that defies reality. This mysterious abode, crafted by a genius lost to history, is a maze of shifting rooms and enigmatic puzzles. Each chamber presents a piece of a cryptic tale, leading them deeper into the fabric of an unseen world. With time slipping away, they must unravel the secrets that weave through the mansion's heart, where the 13th exit holds the key to their escape.

name: The Dollhouse
description: On the outskirts of town there is an old mansion once owned by a wealthy collector and his family. After the mysterious disappearance of his wife, he shut himself away and he and his daughter were never seen again. Strange sounds coming from the mansion and odd disappearances around town caused rumours to spread that the Collector had a dark secret. Despite the rumours, no one had ever been brave enough to investigate the mansion… until now. Not long after entering, you are quickly subdued by the Collector and left unconscious. After some time, you open your eyes…

name: The Carnival (PG)
description: A spectacular Carnival has arrived in town, and you've all come to see the main attraction: the Fortune Teller. However, upon entering you find yourselves transported into a world of treacherous delights, and mysterious creatures. You are trapped in the Carnival and your only chance of escape is to find the Fortune Teller and have your fate revealed! Will you escape in the time he has given you? Or will you be cursed to wander the Carnival forever?
location: Calgary, Edmonton, Oshawa, Toronto Downtown, Midnight Arcade

name: The Legend of the House
description: On a stormy night, you and your team have decided to sneak into the house to uncover the mystery within, and to find the missing family member. As you’re walking in, you hear a loud bang. The door won’t budge. The barking is approaching...
location: Ajax Kanata Markham Niagara Falls Mississauga Guelph 7734 Hound Lane (14A)

name: The Noir
description: I always heard stories about my grandfather. About how great of a detective he was, about all the lives lost that he avenged by seeking justice for them. But there was one story that never had an ending: the year was 1947, 4 gangsters were found dead in a dive bar owned by the mob. Grandad was assigned to the case to find the person responsible for this almost admirable crime. He had 4 suspects, each more likely a culprit than the last. I never got a chance to hear the ending to this story, if only I could see things through grandad’s eyes and find the ending myself…
location: Ajax Kanata Newmarket Toronto Downtown Vaughan Windsor The Noir (14A)

name: The Lab: Lockdown
description: Our Most Popular Theme Loved by players of all levels. Beginner-Friendly Perfect for first-time escape room adventurers. Innovative Puzzles Breaks away from the typical escape room formula. Immersive Experience Dive into a storyline that keeps you fully engaged! Immersive and Realistic Design Every element fits logically into the story, creating a highly believable and engaging experience with multiple endings. Unique and Creative Puzzles Puzzles are logical, and offer multiple solutions, encouraging creativity and teamwork. Physical and Technical Challenges Includes tasks requiring physical coordination and basic programming skills, making it diverse and dynamic.
location: 3478 Lawrence Ave. E. Unit C06, Toronto

name: The Tomb: Raiders of the Sword
description: Offers approximately 75% of the full experience, with a more affordable price. Some rooms, challenges and props are omitted, and costumes are not provided.

name: THE LAB : LOCKDOWN
description: Our most popular game! You're locked in a secret lab. You have 60 minutes to find clues and solve puzzles to escape before the clock runs out.

name: THE TOMB: RAIDERS OF THE SWORD
description: You're trapped in an ancient tomb filled with traps and puzzles. The only way out is to find the legendary sword and escape before the tomb's curse consumes you within 60 minutes.

name: The Mystery of the Haunted Mansion
description: Explore a spooky mansion filled with secrets and solve riddles to escape the curse.

name: The Secret Chamber
description: Deep within an ancient castle lies a secret chamber hidden from the world for centuries. You have one hour to uncover its secrets before the door locks forever.

name: The Mystery of Dr. Brain
description: You and your team are in a race against time to stop Dr. Brain's evil plan. Solve puzzles, find hidden objects, and unravel the mystery before it's too late.

name: The Secret Agent's Dilemma
description: Discover secret messages, crack codes and outsmart enemy agents in this thrilling spy-themed game.

name: The Heist
description: In this exhilarating game, your team of aspiring thieves must crack codes and solve puzzles to pull off the ultimate heist. Can you outsmart the security system and escape within 60 minutes?

name: The Enigma of the Mansion
description: A century-old mystery awaits in this grand mansion. Solve cryptic puzzles and unravel the secrets hidden within its walls to escape before time runs out.

name: The Haunted Mansion
description: Solve supernatural puzzles and escape this eerie mansion before the witching hour.

name: The Suspense/Suspense/Storyline Activity
description: 2-6 people, $55/person + HST. 60 minutes.

name: The Best 60 Minutes of Your Day
description: Gather your team, put away your phones and transport yourself to another world!

name: The Blind Tiger
description: You have 60 minutes to find their loot… The story was unbelievable! You had heard the rumours since John Dillinger and his gang were killed, the money from their last bank robbery had never been recovered and was hidden somewhere in Chicago. This was a story that you couldn’t ignore...

name: The 13 Doors Escape Room
description: Did the 13 doors escape room! group of 4. we made it out but just in time, about 4 minutes to spare! So a perfect challenge for the hour time slot. Staff was also super fun and friendly and gave a great atmosphere. Will certainly go back for a new room!

name: The Chase
description: THINK! YOU HAVE 60 MINUTES TO SAVE YOUR CREW… The sound of the cannons are deafening as you and your mates cower in the darkness of your cells, praying that the next shot doesn’t come crashing through the hull and send you all to a watery grave. How you ended up a prisoner on Blackbeard’s ship being chased by the Spanish Armada in the middle of the Carribbean is another story, one that you might not live to tell. The ship is badly damaged and won’t survive the hour, there must be a way out of these chains and onto the deck, at least there you will stand a chance. You got the crew into this mess and you MUST get them out. The clock is ticking.

name: The Prison Break
description: You've been framed for a crime you didn't commit and must gather evidence, outsmart the guards, and escape the high-security prison before it's too late.

name: The Secret Agent's Mission
description: You are a secret agent on a mission to defuse a bomb in an enemy's hideout. You have only 60 minutes before the bomb explodes.

name: The Cabin Mystery
description: The light is blinding as your eyes slowly begin to open. The stark white of the room starts to come into focus despite the terrible pounding in your head. Where am I? You see the same look of confusion on the faces of your friends as they begin to awaken all around you ? What is this place? More importantly , How did we get here? The last thing you remember was sitting around the cabin laughing and joking with a glass of wine after dinner and then…. Nothing. WAIT, this isn't everyone, Billy and Crystal were at dinner last night but now they’re GONE.

name: The Haunted Asylum
description: An abandoned asylum is rumored to be haunted. You enter with a group of investigators, but as you delve deeper into the mystery, you realize that something truly evil resides within. Can you solve the puzzles and escape before it's too late?

name: The Toronto Stock Exchange Heist
description: The Toronto Stock Exchange faces an unprecedented threat: a massive hack by the elusive 'Red Masks' group. Their goal? Siphon off vast sums of money undetected, putting the entire nation's economy on the line. The clock is ticking as this financial fortress stands on the brink of chaos. YOUR MISSION Selected for an urgent and crucial task, you must connect with '0xsen', a former 'Red Masks' hacker turned pacifist, now concealed in Old Toronto's historic district. In this outdoor escape game, you'll engage in secure communications with 0xsen to halt the cyber attack on the Toronto Stock Exchange. As you earn his trust and join his cause, you'll be challenged to solve intricate puzzles and decipher enigmas that form a web of high-tech intrigue.

name: The Evil Dragon of Toronto
description: Embark on an epic adventure to stop a dragon menacing Toronto. Navigate iconic sites with speed and caution. This is more than an escape game: it's your chance to become an urban hero.

name: The Jewels of Calgary
description: Dive into an epic outdoor adventure where legends and family secrets collide! Crack each riddle and piece together the clues scattered as you unravel a thrilling family legacy.

name: The Lab
description: A secret government lab has been taken over by a rogue AI. It's up to you and your team to hack the mainframe, override the security system, and shut down the AI before it's too late.

name: The Cabin in the Woods
description: You're trapped in a cabin deep in the woods with no way out. But that's just the beginning of your problems. Something evil is lurking outside, and it wants in.

name: The Mystery of Eldridge Mansion
description: Solve the puzzles in this historic mansion to unravel a century-old mystery. Recommended for ages 12 and up.

name: The Mystery of Room X
description: You have been trapped in a mysterious room and need to solve puzzles to escape within 60 minutes.

name: The Experience
description: This experience far exceeded my expectations and I would wholeheartedly do it again and recommend it to all my friends! Thoroughly enjoyed the experience and will be back to try a new one! The venue, actors, theme was exceptional! Best Escape Room we've ever done! I love escape rooms and experiences, and this one did not disappoint We're all experienced players and it was the BEST any of us have ever done! The actors did an amazing job, and their banter was as a highlight of the room. I enjoyed having multiple actors in the room and would enjoy another room with multiple characters to interact with. The actors were fantastic the entire time. Wow! Really well thought-through escape game with attention to historic details and super immersive.

name: The Perfect Bite murder mystery dinner experience
description: Share the thrill of a one-of-a-kind murder mystery dinner experience in Vancouver with The Perfect Bite eGift card. Perfect for whodunnit fanatics hungry to crack a case. Grab a gift card for your friends and family before tickets vanish!

name: The Village at Black Creek Escape Room
description: Test your courage within the shadowy confines of a historic village alongside its eerie inhabitants. Our actors bring this experience to life. Let their immersive performances pull you into the story at the heart of the village. A real historical village Built within the historical Village at Black Creek, the sets and costumes will whisk you away to a bygone era. Wander the old village after dark and after hours. Your ticket is your key to be whisked away to a time long lost.
price: Price not explicitly stated, but mentioned as 'the price you see listed is for one individual ticket'

name: The Dragon's Song
description: What thou shalt expect Be not afraid, for this journey you are about to embark upon is nothing but an adventure of the mind. Whilst we have brought forth living actors to aid you in your quest, they will not encroach upon your space, and it is your duty to not disturb theirs. Our sets and costumes have been crafted with great care, to transport you to another realm and allow you to lose yourself in the experience.
location: a tower within Casa Loma, a place where only the bravest adventurers and alchemists are worthy to go

name: The Escape Room Adventure
description: Absolutely loved this with a fantastic storyline. I was unsure about doing a puzzle room with strangers, but there were enough puzzles around the room that it was easy to divide and conquer. I also loved the interaction with the actors, they were brilliant and made the escape room truly unique.

name: The Perfect Bite
description: The mysterious one-of-a-kind dinner party provides a fun escape and a chance to dress to impress for an evening. While being entertained, guests will also indulge in a delicious four-course meal at a local French-inspired bistro.

name: The Wedding Party
description: This experience includes a The Wedding Party has Play in teams of up to This reception will last This experience can be “Challenging, fun, immersive, talented actors, multi-stage, good storytelling, great use of players’ cellphones/internet access to add elements. Unique night out!” “One of the things that Secret City does remarkably well is creating fascinating crossover hooks — a pirate boat cruise at sunset, exploring the inner walls of an actual heritage castle, and now a wedding reception.” “This is a night you won’t forget. There’s over 8 fantastic live actors and on top of that, the food was top notch”

name: The Escape Theatre
description: Had an amazing time. The performers and puzzles were great. The venue was great. Would definitely recommend to others. Thanks so much.

name: The Wedding Reception
description: This is a night you won’t forget. There’s over 8 fantastic live actors and on top of that, the food was top notch. It was so much fun! The story and the actors were great. I really enjoyed the puzzles. The puzzles were a perfect balance of challenging but not overly easy or hard. It felt satisfying to solve them and the wide variety of sources we needed to solve them was great... Having to work together with a bunch of strangers on our table really bonded us, and we made a few friends at the end of the event! The venue was great.

name: The Study
description: You are a group of students who have found your professor's hidden study. He has been acting strangely, and you suspect he might be involved in something sinister. You have one hour to uncover the truth before he returns.

name: The Mystery of Dr. Frankenstein's Lab
description: Solve puzzles and riddles to stop Dr. Frankenstein from creating a new monstrous creature in his secret lab.

name: The Zodiac Killer's Lair
description: Unlock clues hidden in a serial killer's lair to stop him from striking again and escape before the police arrive.

name: The Mystery of the Lost Treasure
description: Unravel the enigma of the lost treasure in this immersive escape room adventure. With a time limit of 60 minutes, you and your team will need to solve clever puzzles and decipher hidden clues to unveil the secret location of the long-lost riches.

name: The Da Vinci Room
description: Unlock the secrets of Leonardo da Vinci in our most challenging room, The Da Vinci Room. Decipher codes and solve intricate puzzles to discover the genius' hidden masterpiece.

name: The Jester's Game
description: Enter the twisted world of a deranged jester in this immersive escape room adventure. Can you unravel his cryptic jokes and riddles to bring order back to his chaotic mind? Expect the unexpected as you navigate through a series of laugh-out-loud challenges.

name: The Submarine
description: You are part of an elite team tasked with investigating a mysterious underwater distress signal. As you dive deeper into the abyss, your submarine malfunctions, leaving you stranded at the bottom of the ocean. With only 60 minutes worth of oxygen left, can you repair the sub and make it back to safety?

name: The Secret of the Old Mansion
description: In this classic escape room scenario, you and your team are trapped in an old mansion filled with hidden passages and secret compartments. You must solve a series of puzzles to find the key to escape within 60 minutes.

name: The Mystery of Blackwood Manor
description: You've been invited to a weekend getaway at the seemingly quiet Blackwood Manor, but things quickly take a dark turn as you uncover secrets and try to unravel the mystery behind the disappearance of its owner.

name: The Heist: Artful Escape
description: Assemble a crew and attempt to pull off the perfect art heist at the renowned Museum of Curiosities. Can you outwit the security systems and make off with the coveted painting without getting caught?

name: The Lost Treasure of Captain Blackheart
description: You're a crew aboard the infamous pirate ship, The Serpent's Revenge. Captain Blackheart has hidden his treasure somewhere on board and it's your mission to find it before time runs out.

name: The Labyrinth of Dr. Paradox
description: Dr. Paradox has created a labyrinthine lair filled with riddles, traps, and mind-bending puzzles. Can you navigate his maze and defeat him before it's too late?

name: The Haunting of Hill House
description: You've been called to investigate strange occurrences in the infamous Hill House. Explore the eerie mansion, unravel its dark past, and confront the terrifying entities that reside within.

name: The Time Travel Paradox
description: A malfunctioning time machine has sent you back to a pivotal moment in history. To return to your own time, you must correct the timeline by solving period-specific puzzles and avoiding altering the past.

name: The Secret Society
description: Join a secret society to protect an ancient artifact from falling into the wrong hands. Ages 8 and up.

name: The Haunted Asylum: Escape the Mad Doctor
description: Dr. Schmidt, a mad scientist, has locked you in his asylum for experiments. You must find your way out by solving puzzles and escaping before he returns to claim another victim.

name: The Mystery of Ancient Egypt
description: You find yourself in the heart of ancient Egypt, surrounded by hieroglyphs and puzzles. Your mission is to solve the mysteries of this lost civilization before time runs out.

name: The Enigma of St. Mary's
description: A local legend speaks of a mysterious treasure hidden deep within the ancient walls of St. Mary’s Church, waiting to be discovered by those brave enough to unlock its secrets.

name: The Mystery of the Vanishing Act
description: A renowned magician has disappeared without a trace, leaving behind only an empty stage and a cryptic message. It's up to you to unravel the magic and find out what happened.

name: The Smurfs: Blueberry Blast
description: In this Smurfs VR game, step into the vibrant Smurf Village and defend it from enemies like Gargamel and his minions using a trusty slingshot.

name: The Secret Laboratory
description: Dr. E has gone mad and locked everyone in his secret laboratory! Solve puzzles to escape before Dr. E returns.

name: The Grand Wilshire Hotel
description: Where guests check in, but may not always check out! Enter the abandoned Grand Wilshire Hotel and meet the ghost that haunts it – Dr. Herman Mudgett. Inside are three trapped souls awaiting their release! You have 1 hour to rescue them. If you don’t succeed then you will be trapped with them forever in the haunted cavern that is – The Grand Wilshire Hotel!

name: The Wrath of Amun Ra
description: The World is in Turmoil! The Egyptian God Amun Ra is angry and has placed a curse on modern day civilization. A catastrophic storm will soon wreak havoc on the earth! You and your team have one hour to enter the Ancient Temple of Ramesses and lift the curse. Armageddon is near as the doomsday clock starts ticking!

description: Deep in the woods, you've found an old, abandoned cabin. Rumors say it's haunted by the spirit of a miner who was murdered there a century ago. You have 60 minutes to solve the puzzles inside before the ghostly presence returns.

name: The Escape Game

description: Infiltrate an art gallery and steal a priceless diamond. Can you pull off the perfect heist?

name: The Haunting

name: The Lost Treasure of Dr. Strangethorp
description: Dr. Strangethorp, a renowned archaeologist, has gone missing while on an expedition to find the lost treasure of Atlantis. Your team must solve puzzles and riddles left behind by Dr. Strangethorp in order to locate the treasure and unravel the mystery of his disappearance.

name: The Lab: Chemical Experiments Gone Wrong
description: A mad scientist's chemical experiments have gone awry, and the lab is now filled with deadly gases. Your team must work together to solve puzzles and escape before you run out of breathable air.

name: The Haunted Mansion Escape Room
description: In this spine-tingling escape room, you'll enter a haunted mansion filled with secrets and scares. Can your team solve the puzzles and break the curse before time runs out?

name: The Escape Artist
